					<li><p>addition rule</p></li>
					<li><p>combination</p></li>
					<li><p>factorial</p></li>
					<li><p>inclusion/exclusion rule</p></li>
					<li><p>intersection</p></li>
					<li><p>multiplication rule</p></li>
					<li><p>mutually exclusive</p></li>
					<li><p>permutation</p></li>
					<li><p>tree diagram</p></li>
				</ul></p>
			</li>					
			<li><p>accomplish the following tasks:
				<ul>
					<li><p>Use the addition and multiplication counting rules</p></li>
					<li><p>Use the inclusion/exclusion counting rule</p></li>
					<li><p>Correctly compute and use factorials.</p></li>
					<li><p>Correctly apply the permutation counting rule</p></li>
					<li><p>Correctly apply the combination counting rule</p></li>
