	  				<mrow>D = \lbrace a, 2, b \rbrace\amp \qquad E = \lbrace x, a, 3 \rbrace\amp \quad F = \lbrace a, b, c \rbrace</mrow>
	  			</md></p>
	  		<p>Question: Identify each of the following pairs of sets as mutually exclusive or intersecting.
	  			<ol label="a" cols="2">
	  				<li><p><m>A</m> and <m>B</m></p></li>
	  				<li><p><m>B</m> and <m>E</m></p></li>
	  				<li><p><m>C</m> and <m>F</m></p></li>
	  				<li><p><m>B</m> and <m>F</m></p></li>
	  				<li><p><m>A</m> and <m>D</m></p></li>
	  				<li><p><m>E</m> and <m>F</m></p></li>
	  			</ol>
	  		</p>
	  	</statement>
	  	<answer><p><ol label="a">
